title: Dead Hydropower Station [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
The city was left in total darkness. What happened? You are sent to find out why the hydroelectric power station is not working. Once you get to the station, you will find out that all the workers have become monsters. What happened to them? What is behind all of this? Take your weapon and destroy the monster behind the monsters, and restore power.

Control keys:

WASD - Character Movement
SPACEBAR - Jump
SHIFT - Sprint
1,2,3,4,5 ...- Weapon change
R - Reload
Esc - Exit the menu
LMB - Shoot
RMB - Aim


System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 мmb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 671 mb
